## Tipografia
- H1: .fs-60 .fw-700 (Hero titles)
- H2: .fs-45 .fw-600 (Section titles)
- H3: .fs-32 .fw-600 (Subsection titles)
- H4: .fs-24 .fw-500 (Card titles)
- Body: .fs-16 .fw-400 (Regular text)
- Small: .fs-14 .fw-400 (Captions, labels)

